Make sure you have Ansible installed on your control node, which can be your local machine or a remote server dedicated to running Ansible. 
You'll need one Ubuntu 18.04 server to serve as node / host.

Clone this repository
Set up your inventory file - you can use inventory-example as base
Adjust values on your group_vars/all.yml file
Run the server-setup.yml playbook to set up the LEMP server
Run the laravel-deploy.yml playbook to deploy the demo Laravel application
Access your server's IP address or hostname to test the setup